data.description: "A Rocking Chair Friendly Front Porch" comes with this 3 bedroom, 2 bath 1,511 heated square foot home on a corner lot in Remington Estates. I-20 accessible from Wells Rd. Or Exit 108. There are granite counter tops, laminate wood and tile floors throughout and new roof was installed in 2016. The 2 nice storage buildings in the fenced in back yard remain also. The remaining furniture in home (3 piece BR suite, currio cabinet, cherry wood desk and chester drawers ) has price tags on them are for sale to the general public. Call me or your favorite realtor to take a "see" cruise of this neat home.
